description:
Make BEGIN IMMEDIATE transaction mode configurable. Currently hardcoded in base.py (lines 293-298), users cannot opt-out for specific transaction requirements.

Location: packages/litefs-django/src/litefs_django/db/backends/litefs/base.py

Action:
1. Add OPTIONS to Django database config:
   DATABASES = {
       'default': {
           'ENGINE': 'litefs_django.db.backends.litefs',
           'OPTIONS': {
               'litefs_mount_path': '/var/lib/litefs',
               'transaction_mode': 'IMMEDIATE',  # or 'DEFERRED' (default SQLite)
           },
       }
   }

2. Update get_new_connection() to read transaction_mode from settings_dict OPTIONS

3. Apply mode at transaction level, not connection level (PRAGMA read_uncommitted, BEGIN mode)

Verification: Tests pass with both IMMEDIATE and DEFERRED modes
